  <titles>
    <title as="introduced" type="short">Surviving Spouses and Dependents Outreach Enhancement and Veterans Casework Improvement Act</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To amend title 38, United States Code, to enhance outreach programs carried out by the Department of Veterans Affairs to provide for more fully informing eligible surviving spouses and dependents of deceased veterans of benefits available to them under laws administered by the Secretary of Veterans Affairs and to improve assistance provided at local levels by providing for staff with specific responsibilities to assist those individuals in obtaining benefits under those laws.</title>
